Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:33.04,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an7}♪ 今晚你属于我 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Tonight you're mine completely ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:42.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an7}♪ 你把爱给得温柔如蜜 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ You give your love so sweetly ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:53.67,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an7}♪ 今夜你眼里有爱的光辉 ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Tonight the light of love is in your eyes ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:03.63,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\an7}♪ 但明天你还会爱我吗？ ♪\N{\rLyricsEng}♪ Will you still love me tomorrow? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等...\N{\rEng}One minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快派个人去那里\N{\rEng}Get somebody down there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 您还好吗？\N{\rEng}Ma'am, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.54,0:01:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,您能听见我说话吗？\N{\rEng}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,南草坪上有人受伤 \N{\rEng}I got someone on the south lawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要急救人员立刻过来\N{\rEng}we need paramedics over here right away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rEng}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 你这是怎么了？\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 婆家 - 你说是婆家吗？\N{\rEng}- In-laws. - Did you say in-laws?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的婆家怎么了？女士\N{\rEng}What about your in-laws, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿 别昏过去\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, hey, stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,睁眼看着我\N{\rEng}Just keep your eyes on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,放松\N{\rEng}Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢呼吸\N{\rEng}Slow, steady breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 哇 哇\N{\rEng}Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她倒下了\N{\rEng}She's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把担架抬过来\N{\rEng}Get that stretcher over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先把她抬上去 数到三一起抬\N{\rEng}Get her loaded up. On my count, one hand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,情况危急\N{\rEng}Critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？\N{\rEng}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 三\N{\rEng}One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 抬\N{\rEng}One, two... Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,挺住\N{\rEng}Stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着么？\N{\rEng}She in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给她测一下生命体征\N{\rEng}Let's get a set of vitals on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就给她接氧气\N{\rEng}I'm gonna get oxygen on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,氧气面罩已戴好\N{\rEng}Mask's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要检查一下瞳孔\N{\rEng}I'm gonna check pupils.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,体位性低血压\N{\rEng}Orthostatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,血压测不出\N{\rEng}I don't have a pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瞳孔无反应\N{\rEng}No pupil response.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,检测脉搏\N{\rEng}Let's check her pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,无脉博\N{\rEng}No pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她发生了心脏骤停\N{\rEng}She's in cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,开始胸外按压\N{\rEng}Starting compressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,充电中\N{\rEng}Charging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,200焦耳\N{\rEng}Two hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,准备\N{\rEng}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,清场\N{\rEng}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,正在运送一名体位性低血压的白人女性\N{\rEng}Ortho coming in with a Caucasian female.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,年龄在二十五岁左右\N{\rEng}Mid to late twenties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,处于严重休克状态\N{\rEng}In severe shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,多处撕裂伤\N{\rEng}Multiple lacerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,左手中可能有枪伤\N{\rEng}Possible gunshot wound through the left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹贯穿\N{\rEng}Through and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,脉搏？\N{\rEng}Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,无脉博\N{\rEng}No pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就继续做胸外按压\N{\rEng}I'll get her compressions again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,充电中\N{\rEng}Charging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,200焦耳\N{\rEng}Two hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,清场\N{\rEng}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 捉迷藏？ - 逮到她了\N{\rEng}- Hide and seek？ - She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮你检测\N{\rEng}I'll test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一\N{\rEng}Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会明白的\N{\rEng}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:59.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}《准准备好了没2：我来了》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.38,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2}字幕贡献者\Npubuqi（SubHD）\NBorcolasky（SubHD）\N小p（蒙太奇字幕组）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,勒多马斯太太？\N{\rEng}Mrs. Le Domas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哪里？\N{\rEng}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您现在位于康涅狄格州的伍德伯里\N{\rEng}You're in Woodbury, Connecticut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,圣约翰医院\N{\rEng}St. John's Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么给我戴手铐\N{\rEng}Why am I handcuffed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 勒多马斯夫人 - 叫我麦考利小姐\N{\rEng}- Mrs. Le Domas. - It's Ms. MacCaullay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这里写着您嫁给了亚历克斯·勒多马斯\N{\rEng}It says here you married an Alex Le Domas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那段婚姻没能维持下去\N{\rEng}It didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是罗杰·巴塞特警探\N{\rEng}I'm Detective Roger Bassett.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你有麻烦了 麦考利女士\N{\rEng}You're in some trouble, Ms. MacCaullay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你现已被伍德伯里警察局拘留\N{\rEng}You're being detained by the Woodbury Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,涉嫌纵火和谋杀\N{\rEng}Under suspicion of arson and murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,扑灭大火后 他们在屋内发现了\N{\rEng}They found the remains of two people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,两具遗体\N{\rEng}after they put out the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的衣服上沾满了鲜血\N{\rEng}And your clothes were drenched in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,并且那不是你的血\N{\rEng}It wasn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意做个陈述\N{\rEng}Now, if you'd care to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我支烟吗\N{\rEng}Could you pass me a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考利女士 这对你可没什么好处\N{\rEng}This is not going to go well for you, Ms. MacCaullay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你配合 事情会好办很多\N{\rEng}Things would go a lot easier if you would just cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来看她\N{\rEng}She has a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在等人吗？\N{\rEng}Are you expecting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你\N{\rEng}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这里干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我还是你的紧急联系人\N{\rEng}Well, I'm still your emergency contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\rEng}So, thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？\N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝·麦考利\N{\rEng}Faith MacCaullay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你又是谁？\N{\rEng}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人？\N{\rEng}Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,生物学意义上 对 我们是姐妹\N{\rEng}Biologically speaking, yeah, we're sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不是一家人\N{\rEng}but we're not family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你们几分钟时间\N{\rEng}I'm going to give you a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我会带你去警局\N{\rEng}Then I'm going to take you to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,做陈述\N{\rEng}Get that statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会信的\N{\rEng}You wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这话可能没错 但我大老远开车\N{\rEng}That's probably true, but I drove all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,来到康涅狄格这个鬼地方\N{\rEng}the way out to bumfuck Connecticut,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以... - 你从哪儿来的？\N{\rEng}- so... - Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是我住在哪里吗？\N{\rEng}You mean, where do I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,默里山\N{\rEng}Murray Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在在切尔西\N{\rEng}I'm in Chelsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,酷\N{\rEng}Yeah, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在纽约住了多久了\N{\rEng}How long have you lived in New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我十八岁时搬过去的\N{\rEng}I moved out there when I was 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你一样\N{\rEng}Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你竟然从没想过... - 格蕾丝 得了吧\N{\rEng}- And you never thought... - Grace, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前你就说得很清楚了\N{\rEng}You made it very clear a long time ago that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想做我的姐姐 好吗？\N{\rEng}you're not interested in being my sister, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是这么想的\N{\rEng}And the feeling's mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这里不是为了重聚\N{\rEng}I'm not here for a reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好 见到你我也很高兴\N{\rEng}Yeah, it's good to see you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗？\N{\rEng}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我他妈好极了 - 是吗？\N{\rEng}- I'm fucking amazing. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真好极了\N{\rEng}Yeah, really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在做自媒体\N{\rEng}I'm a social media coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我住在一间超棒的一居室里\N{\rEng}I live in a kick-ass one bedroom and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个帅得要命的男朋友 叫德里克\N{\rEng}I have a hot-as-fuck boyfriend named Derek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我不用靠跟你的亚历克斯·勒多马斯上床来得到这些\N{\rEng}And I didn't have to fuck Alex Le Domas to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠我自己的努力\N{\rEng}I did it all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道亚历克斯\N{\rEng}How do you know about Alex?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次我在第七大道二十五街的\N{\rEng}I saw you together once at
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全食超市看到你们在一起\N{\rEng}the Whole Foods on 25th and 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他很高\N{\rEng}He's tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以打个招呼的\N{\rEng}You could have said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我活的那么好\N{\rEng}I'm in a good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛去见你这个唠叨鬼\N{\rEng}You're a negative person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不是唠叨鬼\N{\rEng}I'm not a negative person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尽管你抛弃了我 - 我没有抛弃你\N{\rEng}- And even though you abandoned me... - I did not abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我依然相信人性的善良\N{\rEng}I still believe in the fundamental goodness of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 如果你知道我刚才经历了什么...\N{\rEng}Oh my God, if you knew what I'd just been through...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那就告诉我吧\N{\rEng}Then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过 你不会相信的\N{\rEng}I told you you wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你没事就好\N{\rEng}Alright, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还是这个苦瓜脸\N{\rEng}But you haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走\N{\rEng}I'm just gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝 等一下\N{\rEng}Faith, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼结束后 亚历克斯告诉我 我得抽一张牌\N{\rEng}After the wedding, Alex tells me I have to pull a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,玩上面写的任何游戏\N{\rEng}Play whatever game it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,某种...\N{\rEng}Some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,入会仪式\N{\rEng}initiation ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我起初觉得挺奇怪\N{\rEng}Which I thought was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想让他们喜欢我\N{\rEng}But I wanted them to like me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟他们要成为我的新家人了\N{\rEng}because they were gonna be my new family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,总之\N{\rEng}Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我抽到了捉迷藏\N{\rEng}I pull hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 周围人立马安静了\N{\rEng}And it gets real quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,显然\N{\rEng}Because apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一张坏牌\N{\rEng}That's the bad card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们以为必须把我献祭给魔鬼\N{\rEng}And they think they have to try to sacrifice me to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我 有机会赢\N{\rEng}They told me I could win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能躲到天亮\N{\rEng}If I stayed hidden till dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们认为\N{\rEng}But they thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我赢的话\N{\rEng}If I won...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会死\N{\rEng}They'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们开始猎杀我\N{\rEng}So they hunted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\rEng}I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,手中枪了\N{\rEng}Shot through the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,被一个管家打得半死\N{\rEng}Beat to shit by a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,并且我的\N{\rEng}And my...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的丈夫 刺伤了我\N{\rEng}My husband... Stabbed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我撑到了天亮\N{\rEng}But I made it till dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈赢了\N{\rEng}I fucking won.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\rEng}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们死了吗？\N{\rEng}Did they drop dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们爆炸了\N{\rEng}They blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸了？\N{\rEng}They blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们爆炸后 有个男人坐在椅子上\N{\rEng}And then after they blew up, there was a guy in a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他朝我点了点头\N{\rEng}And he nodded at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,椅子上的男人是谁？\N{\rEng}Who was the guy in the chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他是透明的 但我非常确定他是...\N{\rEng}But he was see-through, so I'm pretty sure he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的...\N{\rEng}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定要进监狱了\N{\rEng}You are so going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:12.75,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（战事陷入胶着 结束遥遥无期）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,批准停火\N{\rEng}Approve the ceasefire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.10,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（突发新闻 双方同意停火）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 丹福斯先生\N{\rEng}Good morning, Mr. Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见\N{\rEng}It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些消息\N{\rEng}I have some news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,出去\N{\rEng}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,勒多马斯家族没了\N{\rEng}The Le Domases are no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,佩妮拉\N{\rEng}Pernilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把我的孩子叫来吗？\N{\rEng}Can you find my children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEng}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我转告其他人\N{\rEng}I'll inform the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（今晚有好戏了）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:31.41,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（新娘活下来了 勒多马斯家族失败了 游戏继续）
Comment: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,(Welcome to Shanghai)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rEng}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,马上把我的律师都叫来\N{\rEng}Get all my lawyers here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,马上\N{\rEng}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（进击工作室）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,历经岁月沧桑的古老宅邸合集\N{\rEng}The collection of the weathered houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛特恩堡 夏洛特\N{\rEng}Clothurnburg. Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）别弄他妈的头发了 卡门\N{\rEng}¡Deja el puto pelo, Carmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）操\N{\rEng}¡Coño!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这破玩意谁写的\N{\rEng}Who wrote this shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就即兴发挥吧\N{\rEng}I'll just wing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我按自己的方式来\N{\rEng}I'll do my own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,像往常一样\N{\rEng}Like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）真见鬼\N{\rEng}¡Puta madre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）真是他妈的大好事\N{\rEng}¡Me cago en esta puta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）过来 卡蒂亚\N{\rEng}¡Ven ya, Katia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）哦 天呐\N{\rEng}¡Ay, Dios!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 好了\N{\rEng}Hey, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉威廉 那人搞砸了\N{\rEng}Tell William the guy shot the jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:21.13,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（鲜肉公司）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我了 混蛋\N{\rEng}It's my time, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本森\N{\rEng}Benson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的刀给我\N{\rEng}Bring me my knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的机会\N{\rEng}This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的机会\N{\rEng}This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,勒拜尔万岁\N{\rEng}Le Bail be praised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,开干\N{\rEng}Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,开干\N{\rEng}Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,开干\N{\rEng}Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（丹福斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\rEng}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以勒多马斯家族失败了\N{\rEng}So the Le Domas failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,新娘活下来了\N{\rEng}The bride survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏继续\N{\rEng}The ball is in play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那不公平\N{\rEng}That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的\N{\rEng}It's... it's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\rEng}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,规则就是这样\N{\rEng}It's in the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道该做什么了吧\N{\rEng}You know what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEng}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,像个爷们\N{\rEng}Be a fucking man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了你姓丹福斯\N{\rEng}You're a Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这绝不能离开我们家族\N{\rEng}This... must never leave our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须夺回这个席位\N{\rEng}You must win the seat back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会的\N{\rEng}We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rEng}You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,痛快点吧\N{\rEng}Get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯\N{\rEng}Titus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\N{\rEng}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对新娘来说还没结束\N{\rEng}Not for the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 麦考利夫人\N{\rEng}All right, Mrs. MacCaullay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给你拿些衣服\N{\rEng}We'll get you some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们到警局继续谈话\N{\rEng}Then continue our conversation at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我迫不及待想听你讲那只山羊的事\N{\rEng}I can't wait for you to tell me about that goat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切都会是你的\N{\rEng}It's all gonna be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的规则\N{\rEng}Fuck the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 求您了\N{\rEng}Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,勒多马斯夫人\N{\rEng}Mrs. Le Domas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈什么情况\N{\rEng}What is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这事怎么又开始了\N{\rEng}This can't be happening again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我得有武器\N{\rEng}Listen, I need a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我先回车里拿\N{\rEng}I'm going back to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别抛弃我\N{\rEng}Do not leave me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的\N{\rEng}Okay, Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤到我了\N{\rEng}You hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在的捉迷藏水平也不咋样嘛\N{\rEng}Not so good at hide and seek now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦天呐 搞毛线啊\N{\rEng}Oh my God! What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可能还有更多的人来\N{\rEng}There could be more coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我得把手铐弄开\N{\rEng}I gotta get out of these cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗？\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧走\N{\rEng}We gotta get out of here and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在干什么？\N{\rEng}What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能需要打架\N{\rEng}We might have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着病号服我没法打架\N{\rEng}I can't fight in this gown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间找新衣服了\N{\rEng}No time to look for new clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要打架？\N{\rEng}You have to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的\N{\rEng}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 我们得走了\N{\rEng}Come on, we gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个乱摊子\N{\rEng}What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,威尔金森先生显然想\N{\rEng}Looks like Mr. Wilkinson tried to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在游戏开始前就杀了女孩\N{\rEng}Killed the girl before the game could begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,并让他的整个血脉过早地走向灭亡\N{\rEng}And condemned his entire bloodline to a premature end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 这就是违反拉贝尔先生规则的下场\N{\rEng}Well, that's what happens when you break one of Mr. LaBelle's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你是谁？\N{\rEng}And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那一刻 我知道我们俩都会挺过去的\N{\rEng}And right then I knew that we were both going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们有这一刻值得为之而活\N{\rEng}Because we had this moment to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而如今 我们就在这里\N{\rEng}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了\N{\rEng}We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,马克\N{\rEng}Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我们在化疗病房相遇\N{\rEng}When we met that day in the chemo ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\rEng}Ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常抱歉地告诉你们\N{\rEng}I am terribly sorry to tell you but I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不请你们所有人离开这里\N{\rEng}to have to ask you all to vacate the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 我们出现了煤气泄漏\N{\rEng}Unfortunately, we have a gas leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在开玩笑吗？\N{\rEng}Are you fucking kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有\N{\rEng}She's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请你赶紧滚出去\N{\rEng}Kindly get the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,此外请你礼貌点\N{\rEng}Besides, you could do way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,各位请注意\N{\rEng}Attention ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请根据指示...\N{\rEng}do on procedures...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人该回家了\N{\rEng}These people need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\rEng}Get the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去\N{\rEng}Get the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么总觉得非得当个混蛋不可？\N{\rEng}Why do you always feel the need to be such a dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你但凡有点善意都意义非凡\N{\rEng}Your little grace goes a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那很可笑\N{\rEng}Well, that was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不是搞笑的日子\N{\rEng}Today is not the day for funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸给我们一个任务 我不会让他失望\N{\rEng}Dad gave us a mission and I'm not going to let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,呦\N{\rEng}Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,表亲们\N{\rEng}Cousins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,已经过去多久了？\N{\rEng}How long has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我先报个名\N{\rEng}I'm gonna sign it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好戏开场时来叫我\N{\rEng}Come get me when the fireworks start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,摸你鸡鸡\N{\rEng}Dick tap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必跟他说话\N{\rEng}You don't have to speak to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别惹事 行吗？\N{\rEng}Just don't start anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天别惹事\N{\rEng}Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的基普\N{\rEng}Fucking Kip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们非做不可\N{\rEng}It had to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤心的时候看起来真像他\N{\rEng}You look just like him when you're sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我再说一遍 请保持冷静 有序地走向出口\N{\rEng}I'll repeat, please remain calm and proceed to the exits in an orderly fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 收拾好你们的破烂 滚出去\N{\rEng}Ladies and gentlemen, pack up your shit and get the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请快点\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,委员会上次举行现场会议是什么时候？\N{\rEng}When was the last time the council actually convened in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1963年10月\N{\rEng}October, 1963.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我查过了\N{\rEng}I looked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他们现在正前往小屋的路上\N{\rEng}Well, they're on their way to the lodge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了\N{\rEng}And so it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伊格纳西奥\N{\rEng}Ignacio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,费利佩\N{\rEng}Felipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 丹福斯夫人\N{\rEng}Buenos Días, Senora Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.02,0:23:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点没老\N{\rEng}You haven't aged a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,弗朗西丝卡没来吗？\N{\rEng}No Francesca?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本以为她肯定想亲眼见证这一刻\N{\rEng}I thought for sure she'd want to be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她马上就来 相信我\N{\rEng}She'll be along, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会错过这个的\N{\rEng}She wouldn't miss this for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是件好事\N{\rEng}It's exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 对我来说真是件好事\N{\rEng}it's exciting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说不是\N{\rEng}It's terrifying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对 还有你\N{\rEng}Yes, and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 费利佩\N{\rEng}Vamos, Felipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,乌苏拉\N{\rEng}Ursula.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯\N{\rEng}Titus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得我儿子吗？承福\N{\rEng}You remember my son? Cheng Fu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,认识你承福 欢迎\N{\rEng}I know you, Chengfu. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wi-Fi密码是什么？\N{\rEng}What's the Wi-Fi password?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.40,0:24:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,态度好点儿\N{\rEng}Be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.65,0:24:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,马杜\N{\rEng}Madhu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,维拉杰\N{\rEng}Viraj
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,玛蒂娜 欢迎\N{\rEng}Martina, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,规则是什么？\N{\rEng}So how's this shit work?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大家马上到齐了 到时候律师会向大家说明一切\N{\rEng}Our guests will be arriving soon, and then the lawyer will explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.65,0:24:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 大律师\N{\rEng}Ah, lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟这边这位漂亮笨蛋说话慢点\N{\rEng}Speak slow for this beautiful dum-dum over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.30,0:24:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,爆破音\N{\rEng}Single-syllable words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们的贵宾要到了\N{\rEng}It appears our guest of honor is arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.55,0:24:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Hello, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.03,0:25:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是乌苏拉·丹福斯\N{\rEng}I'm Ursula Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.67,0:25:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我哥哥泰特斯\N{\rEng}This is my brother Titus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.25,0:25:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我们家\N{\rEng}Welcome to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.18,0:25:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲 我可以跟她说话吗\N{\rEng}May I speak to her, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.85,0:25:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）可以 可以 去吧 费利佩\N{\rEng}Sí, sí, ándale, Felipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.95,0:25:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,它伤不着你\N{\rEng}It can't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.49,0:25:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你见到勒贝尔先生了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you see Mr. LeBail?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.44,0:25:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rEng}One second.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在开始之前 我得先拍张自拍\N{\rEng}I just gotta take a quick selfie before we start.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呦\N{\rEng}Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.78,0:25:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这女孩打败了勒多马斯家族\N{\rEng}This girl bested the Le Domases.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.13,0:25:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还有比尔·威尔金森\N{\rEng}And Bill Wilkinson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.57,0:25:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能开始了吗？\N{\rEng}Can we start this, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,切斯特他妈在哪儿？\N{\rEng}And where the fuck is Chester?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.58,0:25:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的父亲...去世了\N{\rEng}Our father... passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.07,0:25:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.00,0:25:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.99,0:25:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚 在睡梦中\N{\rEng}Last night, in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.28,0:25:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\rEng}Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.09,0:25:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那意味着你现在要参赛了\N{\rEng}So does that mean that you're playing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.58,0:25:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们是双胞胎 那我们俩都会上场 对吧？\N{\rEng}As we are twins, we will both be taking the field, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.09,0:25:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.11,0:25:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.66,0:25:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,多方便啊\N{\rEng}How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.10,0:25:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）我早就跟你说过 丹福斯一家都是阴险小人\N{\rEng}Te dije que los Danforths son unas víboras.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.35,0:25:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）没事的\N{\rEng}Está bien.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.92,0:25:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）他们在耍诡计\N{\rEng}Y que iban a hacer trampas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.31,0:25:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）行了 别担心\N{\rEng}Ya, no te preocupes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.10,0:25:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我明白这对你来说一定很可怕\N{\rEng}Grace, I realize this must be terrifying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但你来到这里 是因为一个非常特别\N{\rEng}But you are here for a very special,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.63,0:25:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,非常令人兴奋的原因\N{\rEng}very exciting reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.77,0:26:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,勒多马斯夫人 您可真是掀起了不小的风波\N{\rEng}You've caused quite a stir, Mrs. Le Domas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.81,0:26:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫麦考利\N{\rEng}MacCaullay!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.57,0:26:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我是拉贝尔先生和拉贝尔组织的唯一律师\N{\rEng}I am the sole attorney for Mr. LaBelle and the LaBelle organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.88,0:26:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,该组织由一个理事会领导 该理事会由六个家族的首领组成\N{\rEng}The organization is led by a council made up of the heads of six families,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.71,0:26:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,包括你的婆家\N{\rEng}including your in-laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.66,0:26:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在德莫斯和威尔金森家族已经被消灭\N{\rEng}Now The DeMoss and Wilkinson families have been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.66,0:26:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,六大家族议会目前缩减到四个\N{\rEng}The council of six families is currently down to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.50,0:26:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里的原因是\N{\rEng}The reason you're here is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.63,0:26:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你从勒德莫斯家的捉迷藏游戏中幸存下来\N{\rEng}that by surviving Le DeMoss' game of hide and seek,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.94,0:27:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你触发了我们组织章程中一条\N{\rEng}you triggered a very seldom use
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.89,0:27:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,极少被援引的条款\N{\rEng}clause in our organization's bylaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 在理事会中\N{\rEng}You see, on the council there is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.65,0:27:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个席位的权力比其他席位更大\N{\rEng}one seat with more power than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.26,0:27:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,至高席位\N{\rEng}The high seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.62,0:27:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,它配有这个权力徽章\N{\rEng}And it comes with this, sigil of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.71,0:27:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,直到现在 那个席位由切斯特·丹福斯占据\N{\rEng}Until now, that seat was occupied by Chester Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你听说过他\N{\rEng}I presume you've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.62,0:27:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你触发了那个条款 至高席位现在空缺了\N{\rEng}Because you triggered that clause, the high seat is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.40,0:27:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很多很多年来的第一次\N{\rEng}now vacant for the first time in many, many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.53,0:27:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 信不信由你\N{\rEng}And, believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.71,0:27:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你获得了一个赢得至高席位的机会\N{\rEng}you've been given an opportunity to win the high seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.66,0:27:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,能从游戏中幸存下来的人非常少 \N{\rEng}It's very rare that someone survives a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.59,0:27:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以会获得这份奖励\N{\rEng}so it comes with this reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.54,0:27:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,其余议会家族的首领们\N{\rEng}And the heads of the remaining council families
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.37,0:27:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也会竭力争夺这个席位\N{\rEng}will try to win the seat for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.21,0:27:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,或者就我们而言 夺回本应属于我们的东西\N{\rEng}Or in our case, take back what should still be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个条款真他妈蠢\N{\rEng}This clause is so fucking stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.44,0:27:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你是怕我们其中一个会取代你爸爸的位置 是吗？\N{\rEng}Ah, you're afraid one of us is going to take Daddy's place, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.08,0:27:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢\N{\rEng}You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.44,0:27:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,勒德莫斯夫人可能会赢\N{\rEng}Mrs. Le DeMoss could win.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.65,0:28:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 正如丹福斯女士所说 这其实全是好消息\N{\rEng}So, as Ms. Danforth said, this is all actually good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.87,0:28:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,勒贝尔先生向你展示了笑颜\N{\rEng}Mr. LeBail has smiled upon thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.86,0:28:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,赞美撒旦\N{\rEng}Hail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.29,0:28:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,赞美撒旦\N{\rEng}Hail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.79,0:28:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,赞美撒旦\N{\rEng}Hail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\rEng}Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.37,0:28:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么问题吗？\N{\rEng}have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.39,0:28:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我有\N{\rEng}I have
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.32,0:28:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我一支烟吗？\N{\rEng}Can I have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.84,0:28:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.53,0:28:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹的出现真是个意外\N{\rEng}Your sister's existence was quite a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉勒多马斯家族你没有家人 然而 费丝在这里\N{\rEng}You told the Le Domas that you had no family, and yet, here is faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.06,0:28:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝和费丝 他妈的爱尔兰天主教名字\N{\rEng}Grace and faith, fucking Irish Catholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.74,0:28:52.50,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}【译注: 格蕾丝英语意为赞美 费丝意为信念】
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.54,0:28:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\rEng}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.14,0:28:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们赶紧结束吧\N{\rEng}We can make this real quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我他妈的才不要你的席位\N{\rEng}because I don't want your fucking chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.11,0:29:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我没有说清楚\N{\rEng}I suppose I wasn't clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.91,0:29:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,至高席位控制议会 议会控制着\N{\rEng}The high seat controls the council, and the council controls...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.85,0:29:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一切\N{\rEng}well, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.79,0:29:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一切？\N{\rEng}Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.06,0:29:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,整个世界\N{\rEng}The world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.23,0:29:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样 我就得再抽一张牌之类的吗？\N{\rEng}So what, I just have to pull another card or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.69,0:29:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那个必要\N{\rEng}That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.93,0:29:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把它想成双倍或全输的赌局吧\N{\rEng}Think of this as double or nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.12,0:29:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你从勒多马斯家族的捉迷藏游戏中\N{\rEng}Because you survived Le Domas' game of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.04,0:29:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,幸存下来 你将再次玩那个游戏\N{\rEng}hide and seek, you will play that game again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.23,0:29:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.03,0:29:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这次 是和议会成员一起\N{\rEng}This time, with the council members.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.72,0:29:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的小屁孩\N{\rEng}Fucking baby shit bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.27,0:29:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我怎么赢？\N{\rEng}So for me to win the seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.66,0:29:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,活到天亮\N{\rEng}Survive until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.98,0:29:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人呢？\N{\rEng}And the rest of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.94,0:29:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这部分你很熟悉\N{\rEng}This part will be familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.33,0:29:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将会杀死你\N{\rEng}They will try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.69,0:29:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谁杀了你 赢得至高位\N{\rEng}Whoever does, wins the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们必须在天亮前填补这个空缺\N{\rEng}Now, we must fill the seat by dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.99,0:29:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,否则勒贝尔先生就会...\N{\rEng}or Mr. LeBail will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.90,0:29:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不高兴\N{\rEng}very upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.24,0:29:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 获胜者将... - 太棒了\N{\rEng}- The winner will... - Ah! Fuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.03,0:30:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,臭孩子\N{\rEng}You silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.07,0:30:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,赞美撒旦\N{\rEng}Hail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.32,0:30:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,获胜者将在黑神庙\N{\rEng}The winner will be coronated in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.60,0:30:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,举行的特别仪式上加冕\N{\rEng}a special ceremony in the Black Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.91,0:30:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,勒贝尔先生最虔诚的信徒们\N{\rEng}The crème de la crème of Mr. LeBail's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.45,0:30:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,将悉数到场\N{\rEng}faithful will be in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.11,0:30:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些\N{\rEng}That's the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.13,0:30:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不玩\N{\rEng}I'm not playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.04,0:30:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 对不起\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.41,0:30:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事\N{\rEng}That's the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.37,0:30:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不玩\N{\rEng}I'M NOT PLAYING!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.78,0:30:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须参赛\N{\rEng}You have to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.80,0:30:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是不玩\N{\rEng}I'm still not playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.81,0:30:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.18,0:30:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,普鲁内拉 杀了那个妹妹\N{\rEng}Prunella, kill the sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.61,0:30:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\rEng}NO! NO! NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.71,0:30:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,操你妈的\N{\rEng}FUCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.05,0:30:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别伤害她\N{\rEng}DON'T HURT HER!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.81,0:30:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把这个拿掉\N{\rEng}You can take that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\rEng}Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.77,0:30:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看起来都是好人\N{\rEng}You guys seem like good people!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.98,0:30:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我甚至都不知道自己为什么会在这里\N{\rEng}And I don't even know why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.60,0:30:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大概有七年没见过了\N{\rEng}We haven't seen each other in, like, seven years!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.55,0:31:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不见面？\N{\rEng}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.87,0:31:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这很复杂\N{\rEng}It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.80,0:31:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好手段啊 蠢货\N{\rEng}Nice leverage, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.03,0:31:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她根本不在乎那个女的\N{\rEng}This thing doesn't even care about the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.10,0:31:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个合不来？\N{\rEng}You two don't get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.77,0:31:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们闹翻了\N{\rEng}We had a falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.81,0:31:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为什么？\N{\rEng}About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.27,0:31:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为她是个混蛋\N{\rEng}Just her being an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.47,0:31:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 让我总结一下\N{\rEng}Look, allow me to wrap up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.23,0:31:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏将在下午2点31分准时开始\N{\rEng}The game will begin at exactly 2:31 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.27,0:31:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为遵守拉贝尔先生所指定的确切时间...\N{\rEng}In observance of the exact time Mr.LaBelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.48,0:31:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\rEng}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.02,0:31:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）我的宝贝\N{\rEng}Mi amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.61,0:31:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 天呐 你来了\N{\rEng}Well, holy shit, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.03,0:31:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,弗朗西丝卡·埃尔卡多 你个蠢荡妇\N{\rEng}Francesca El Caído, you dumb slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.76,0:31:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.13,0:31:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯的前未婚妻\N{\rEng}Alex's ex-fiancee.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.54,0:31:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我的戒指他妈在哪 婊子？\N{\rEng}Where the fuck is my ring, bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.81,0:31:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在你偷走他之前 他买给我的\N{\rEng}He bought it for me before you stole him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.07,0:31:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就在他爆炸之前 我把它扔向了他\N{\rEng}I threw it at him right before he exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.81,0:31:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不过是个冷血的婊子\N{\rEng}You're nothing but a cold-hearted whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.15,0:32:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 亚历克斯并不傻 但他确实他妈的太好骗了\N{\rEng}You see, Alex wasn't stupid, but he sure was fucking gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.80,0:32:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你毁了我的生活\N{\rEng}You ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.84,0:32:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而我他妈都不知道你是谁\N{\rEng}And I don't even know who the fuck you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.26,0:32:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,别生气 别生气\N{\rEng}Okay, No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 我们应该行动了\N{\rEng}Ladies and gentlemen, we should get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.91,0:32:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,佩妮拉\N{\rEng}Pernilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.49,0:32:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.53,0:32:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想动手\N{\rEng}I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.11,0:32:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\N{\rEng}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.57,0:32:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想\N{\rEng}I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.17,0:32:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想让你知道 会是我抓住你\N{\rEng}I just want you to know it's going to be me who gets you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.41,0:32:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 懂吗？ - 不 不 不\N{\rEng}- Okay? - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.01,0:32:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 我只是紧急联系人\N{\rEng}No, no, no, I just an Emergency Contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.47,0:32:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,理事会成员必须使用一种\N{\rEng}The council members must use a weapon that existed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.56,0:32:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在其祖先与勒贝尔先生达成协议的时期内\N{\rEng}during the period in which their ancestor...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.12,0:32:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就已存在的武器\N{\rEng}..made his or her bargain with Mr.LeBail.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.16,0:33:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,议会成员不得互相残杀\N{\rEng}The council members are not allowed to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.41,0:33:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们这样做了 即使是意外 勒贝尔先生也会生气\N{\rEng}If they do, even by accident, Mr. LeBail will be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而那家有罪之人的整个家族都将受到惩罚\N{\rEng}And the offending family's entire bloodline will be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.84,0:33:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外 百无禁忌\N{\rEng}Beyond that, anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.62,0:33:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想用血笔\N{\rEng}I... I don't want to use the blood pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你至少可以把它消毒一下吧\N{\rEng}Or can you at least sterilize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.98,0:33:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.53,0:33:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,家族成员可以从俱乐部房间观察过程\N{\rEng}The families may observe the proceedings from the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.13,0:33:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,万一有猎人不幸身亡\N{\rEng}In the unlikely event that any of the hunters should perish,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.46,0:33:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,该家族继承序列中的下一位成员\N{\rEng}the next person in that family's line
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,必须立即接替其位置 投入战斗\N{\rEng}of succession must take their place on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.78,0:33:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运\N{\rEng}Best of luck to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.46,0:34:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不换衣服吗 兄弟？\N{\rEng}Aren't you going to change, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.00,0:34:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.15,0:34:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谁都不需要出去\N{\rEng}None of us are going to have to go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.74,0:34:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,切斯特从孩子们刚会走路起就开始训练他们\N{\rEng}Chester trained his kids since they could walk
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.15,0:34:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,以防这一天真的到来\N{\rEng}in case this day ever came.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.68,0:34:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟内就会结束\N{\rEng}This will be over in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.06,0:34:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那里\N{\rEng}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.70,0:34:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最好是这样\N{\rEng}It better be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我一小时后有个按摩\N{\rEng}I got a massage in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.58,0:34:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这位女孩将从第九洞果岭开始比赛\N{\rEng}The girl will begin the game on the ninth hole green.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.32,0:34:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,猎手们 就位\N{\rEng}Hunters, take your places.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.85,0:34:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏马上开始 十 \N{\rEng}The game will begin in ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.28,0:34:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,九 八 七\N{\rEng}nine, eight, seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.14,0:34:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,六 五 四\N{\rEng}six, five, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,三 二 一\N{\rEng}three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.34,0:34:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没钥匙怎么开\N{\rEng}There are no fucking keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.79,0:34:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我是不是忘记给你们钥匙了？\N{\rEng}Oh, did I forget to put the keys in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.46,0:34:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,操 你作弊\N{\rEng}Fuck. Cheaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.50,0:34:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,开车\N{\rEng}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.53,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 白痴 - 这群傻瓜\N{\rEng}- Idiots - Spoof you, Suckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.97,0:35:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝\N{\rEng}Faith
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.65,0:35:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.74,0:35:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝 快起来\N{\rEng}Faith, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.31,0:35:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 停下\N{\rEng}Please, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.93,0:35:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.72,0:35:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得起来 我们得赶紧走\N{\rEng}We gotta get up. We gotta move.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.96,0:35:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.38,0:35:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得起来\N{\rEng}We gotta get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.42,0:35:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.13,0:35:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我了个天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.08,0:35:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\rEng}They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.71,0:35:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\rEng}They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.24,0:35:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他们想伤害我？\N{\rEng}Why do they want to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.69,0:35:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们根本不在乎你\N{\rEng}They don't give a shit about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.81,0:35:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿只会拖我后腿\N{\rEng}You're here to slow me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.09,0:35:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不按照我说的做 我们将会死\N{\rEng}If you don't do exactly what I say, we are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.53,0:35:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了吗？\N{\rEng}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.52,0:35:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们夺回那个席位后 显然得共享\N{\rEng}So we obviously share the seat when we get it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.33,0:35:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但戒指该谁戴？\N{\rEng}but who gets to wear the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.59,0:35:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 爸爸希望由我来负责 所以...\N{\rEng}Well, Dad wanted me to be the one in charge, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.86,0:35:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,放屁\N{\rEng}Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.25,0:35:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他和我说过\N{\rEng}He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.91,0:36:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他告诉我\N{\rEng}Well, he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.39,0:36:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我来戴戒指\N{\rEng}It should be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.21,0:36:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不 他没有说过\N{\rEng}No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.14,0:36:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要去树林里\N{\rEng}We're gonna get to the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.04,0:36:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要去树林里\N{\rEng}We're gonna go to the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.82,0:36:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等\N{\rEng}Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.64,0:36:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人在树林里等着我们怎么办？\N{\rEng}What if there's people waiting for us in the fucking woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.60,0:36:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\rEng}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.22,0:36:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这没什么好争论的\N{\rEng}It's not a debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.17,0:36:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的算\N{\rEng}I am in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.05,0:36:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你说的算？\N{\rEng}Oh, you're in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.96,0:36:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以在这里 全都是你他妈的错\N{\rEng}It's your fucking fault I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.77,0:36:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是忘了把你从我的紧急联系人名单里移除\N{\rEng}All I did was forget to remove you as my emergency contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.69,0:36:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,七年了\N{\rEng}It's been seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.82,0:36:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不认识其他人吗？\N{\rEng}You don't know anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.15,0:36:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.74,0:36:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,谁杀了她 谁就能戴戒指\N{\rEng}Whoever kills her gets to wear the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\rEng}I'm not agreeing to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.11,0:36:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那他妈是什么\N{\rEng}What the fuck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.01,0:36:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我去\N{\rEng}God!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.03,0:36:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 妈的\N{\rEng}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\rEng}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.75,0:36:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 等等\N{\rEng}Whoa, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.55,0:36:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我是万晨星 \N{\rEng}Listen. This is Wan Chenxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.38,0:36:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前见过\N{\rEng}We met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.07,0:36:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 等等\N{\rEng}Whoa, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个脱离这一切的方法\N{\rEng}There's a way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.30,0:36:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我让律师仔细查阅了章程 结果发现了一个漏洞\N{\rEng}I had my lawyers scour the bylaws and we found a loophole.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.72,0:36:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们所要做的就是...\N{\rEng}All we have to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.47,0:37:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,打得好\N{\rEng}Nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.24,0:37:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,她在那\N{\rEng}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住她\N{\rEng}Get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.25,0:37:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.90,0:37:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rEng}God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.25,0:37:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,斯基皮 打开屏幕\N{\rEng}Skippy, screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.95,0:37:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他们本不该离开果岭的\N{\rEng}They weren't supposed to make it off the green.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.64,0:37:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把那破玩意儿给我\N{\rEng}Give me the fucking thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.72,0:37:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rEng}God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.86,0:37:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有办法过去\N{\rEng}There's no way we're getting over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会有树可以爬的\N{\rEng}There's gotta be a tree we could climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.33,0:37:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我们带着手铐爬树\N{\rEng}Oh, we're gonna climb with handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.68,0:37:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.00,0:37:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 操\N{\rEng}Okay, okay, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.12,0:37:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 打开它\N{\rEng}Okay, turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.49,0:37:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈是什么？\N{\rEng}What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.44,0:37:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不 只需按输入1\N{\rEng}No, just press input one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.64,0:37:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对 不 没错\N{\rEng}Yeah, no, it's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.42,0:37:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我那个该死的输入1\N{\rEng}Show me fucking input one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.22,0:37:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,点击“开始” 然后点击“菜单” 再点击\N{\rEng}Go, press menu, and then go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你们他妈真是蠢透了\N{\rEng}My, you're stupid fucking idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.79,0:37:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她们再他妈哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where the fuck are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.92,0:38:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我们跑了好久了\N{\rEng}Grace, we've been running forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.69,0:38:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,操 嗷 操\N{\rEng}Fuck, ow, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.70,0:38:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你能慢点嘛？\N{\rEng}Can you just slow down, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.96,0:38:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 对不起\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.13,0:38:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.98,0:38:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信你把我卷入到这破事中\N{\rEng}I can't believe you dragged me into this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么发生的？\N{\rEng}How does this even happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.02,0:38:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你不知道你老公信邪教？\N{\rEng}You're telling me you didn't know your fiancé was in a devil cult?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.87,0:38:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这似乎很难不注意到\N{\rEng}Seems kind of hard to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.92,0:38:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你大概只顾着数钱了\N{\rEng}I mean, your attention must have been on all that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.91,0:38:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.01,0:38:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思？\N{\rEng}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.31,0:38:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 我只是说我的钱都是自己挣的\N{\rEng}Nothing, I'm just saying that I work for my shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.14,0:38:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要靠有钱人来解决我的问题\N{\rEng}and I don't need some rich dick to solve my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.32,0:38:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\rEng}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.26,0:38:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\rEng}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.85,0:38:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去你的 - 去你的\N{\rEng}- Fuck you. - Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.93,0:38:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 德里克是做什么的\N{\rEng}Okay, what does Derek do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.41,0:38:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,金融\N{\rEng}Finance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.80,0:38:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那是我在追有钱人？\N{\rEng}Oh, and I'm chasing Rich Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.98,0:38:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚认识的时候 他还是个穷演员\N{\rEng}He was a starving actor when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.43,0:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,饿肚子的演员 还有金融硕士学位？\N{\rEng}Starving actor with a fallback MBA?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.69,0:38:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我是编造了德里克这个人的吗？\N{\rEng}You think I made up Derek?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.30,0:38:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有点 对\N{\rEng}Kinda now, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.70,0:38:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我可悲\N{\rEng}You think I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.11,0:38:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是见不得我混出头 而你没有\N{\rEng}You just can't handle it that I made it and you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.35,0:39:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.20,0:39:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,躲起来没用\N{\rEng}There's no use in hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.87,0:39:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你觉得我们是坏人\N{\rEng}I know you think we're the bad guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.27,0:39:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有好人坏人\N{\rEng}But there are no good guys or bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.09,0:39:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只是体制就是这样的\N{\rEng}There's just the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.70,0:39:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不知你是否意识到了\N{\rEng}Whether you realize it or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.41,0:39:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是这个体制的一部分\N{\rEng}you're a part of it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.76,0:39:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是其中的一分子\N{\rEng}You contribute to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.94,0:39:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在助长它\N{\rEng}How you enable it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.08,0:39:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不比你们更邪恶\N{\rEng}I'm no more evil than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.96,0:39:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不过是某个远比我们宏大的东西的一颗螺丝钉\N{\rEng}We just a small part of something that is much bigger than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.77,0:39:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能行 我们能行 我们能行 我们能行\N{\rEng}We can do it, we can do it, we can do it, we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.89,0:39:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,带着点尊严去死\N{\rEng}And die with a little dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.35,0:40:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,手铐\N{\rEng}Handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.36,0:40:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rEng}Go, go, go! Run, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.86,0:40:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,起来\N{\rEng}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.47,0:40:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行\N{\rEng}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.25,0:40:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你可别搞砸了\N{\rEng}You cannot fuck up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.04,0:40:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要让我们对爸爸所做的一切有意义\N{\rEng}The only way to make what we did to dad mean
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.92,0:40:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的办法就是把那个该死的席位夺回来\N{\rEng}something is to win that fucking seat back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.21,0:40:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯\N{\rEng}Titus!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.26,0:40:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗？\N{\rEng}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.85,0:40:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一的方式\N{\rEng}That is the only way it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.34,0:40:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们去那座楼找个电话\N{\rEng}Let's go to that building and look for a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.10,0:41:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这待得越久 被发现的可能性就越大\N{\rEng}The longer we're on this property, the better there are chances of finding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.70,0:41:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找方法离开这\N{\rEng}We need to figure out a way to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.70,0:41:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,翻过那个墙\N{\rEng}Over that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.07,0:41:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们直接冲过去\N{\rEng}Let's just make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.48,0:41:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那会完全暴露\N{\rEng}It's completely exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.21,0:41:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你太鲁莽了\N{\rEng}You are too impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.40,0:41:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你从不考虑周全\N{\rEng}You never think things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.52,0:41:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 他们也没地方躲\N{\rEng}Look, they don't have anywhere to hide either.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.05,0:41:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你会害死我们俩的\N{\rEng}You're gonna get us both killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.49,0:41:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）现在轮到我了\N{\rEng}Y ahora me toca, toca a mí.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.57,0:41:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）丹福斯一家被我搞定了\N{\rEng}A los Danforth ya los jodí.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.70,0:41:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）你觉得你能赢吗？妹子\N{\rEng}¿Qué vas a ganar, tía?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.67,0:41:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）想的美\N{\rEng}¡Ni eso ni pollos en vinagre!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.68,0:41:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）操白痴\N{\rEng}Joder, gilipollas.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.79,0:41:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这太冒险了\N{\rEng}It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.88,0:41:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这太冒险了\N{\rEng}It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.99,0:41:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,行 好吧 让我先好好想想\N{\rEng}Just, okay, just let me think this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.68,0:41:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候 你得冒一次险\N{\rEng}Sometimes you gotta take a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.62,0:41:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那是枪声吗？\N{\rEng}Is that gunfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.71,0:41:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）终于 终于 终于\N{\rEng}Por fin, ya, ya, ya, por fin
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.43,0:41:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 找到他了\N{\rEng}Oh, found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.67,0:41:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谁他妈在射她们\N{\rEng}Who's fucking shooting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.20,0:42:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸真他妈是个废物\N{\rEng}Your dad fucking sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.90,0:42:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.52,0:42:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他从不练习\N{\rEng}He never practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.59,0:42:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别让她跑了\N{\rEng}If she gets away, I swear to fucking God.
