Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.76,0:43:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我的天呐\N{\rEng}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.35,0:43:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走 走 走\N{\rEng}Let's go, let's go, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.48,0:43:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\rEng}Fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.00,0:43:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦我的天呐\N{\rEng}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.82,0:43:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别看 别看\N{\rEng}Don't look at it, don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.45,0:43:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 不\N{\rEng}No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.54,0:43:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）命真硬啊\N{\rEng}¡De esta libré
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.84,0:43:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\rEng}Okay？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.26,0:43:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.09,0:44:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）狗娘养的\N{\rEng}¡Hijo de la gran puta!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.50,0:44:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.41,0:44:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.47,0:44:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们找到个电话\N{\rEng}Okay. We've got to find a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.49,0:44:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,血都流下来了\N{\rEng}You're leaving a trail of blood behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.46,0:44:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要坐下来\N{\rEng}We need to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.91,0:44:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.79,0:44:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在这\N{\rEng}Sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.73,0:44:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\rEng}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.58,0:44:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.97,0:44:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.83,0:44:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先从小的拔\N{\rEng}Alright, let's do the little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.24,0:44:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一\N{\rEng}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.98,0:44:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,二\N{\rEng}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.24,0:44:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,三\N{\rEng}Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.20,0:44:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\rEng}Just focus on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.32,0:44:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？\N{\rEng}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.95,0:44:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好家伙 你现在还兼职当护士？\N{\rEng}Okay, what are you, a part-time nurse too?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.58,0:45:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是吧\N{\rEng}I don't know, maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.86,0:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你毕业后干什么了\N{\rEng}So, what did you do after you graduated?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.46,0:45:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.93,0:45:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我 呃...我没读完\N{\rEng}I, um, I didn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.95,0:45:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不退学\N{\rEng}I had to drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.56,0:45:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\N{\rEng}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.74,0:45:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 然后我去端盘子\N{\rEng}Yeah, then I waited tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.51,0:45:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说了那么多“追随梦想”的大道理 结果就是这？\N{\rEng}After all that follow your dreams shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.24,0:45:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 有时候梦想就是实现不了\N{\rEng}Yeah, well sometimes dreams don't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.71,0:45:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我遇到了亚历克斯\N{\rEng}And then I met Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.14,0:45:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个梦想也没实现\N{\rEng}And that dream didn't work out either.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.92,0:45:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.77,0:45:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,会有点疼\N{\rEng}It's gonna burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.51,0:45:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.70,0:45:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我找过你\N{\rEng}I tried to find you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.49,0:45:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想邀请你参加婚礼\N{\rEng}I wanted to invite you to a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.43,0:45:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会来的\N{\rEng}I wouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.06,0:45:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不会来 但我想让你知道\N{\rEng}I know, but I wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.89,0:45:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真心想邀请你的\N{\rEng}that I wanted you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.29,0:46:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你绝对没法让我穿上那些\N{\rEng}Well, there's no fucking way you would have got me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.49,0:46:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,丑得要死的伴娘裙 所以\N{\rEng}in one of those ugly-ass bridesmaids' dresses, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.69,0:46:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好了\N{\rEng}Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.59,0:46:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喝点？\N{\rEng}Shot for the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.96,0:46:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.98,0:46:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没什么能减轻跟你在一起的痛苦\N{\rEng}Although nothing's gonna numb the pain of being with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.87,0:46:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为了活到黎明\N{\rEng}To surviving till dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.87,0:46:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次\N{\rEng}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.16,0:47:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 这边\N{\rEng}Come on, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.32,0:47:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我们...\N{\rEng}Okay, we're gonna need...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.07,0:47:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得跟他正面硬刚 我们能对付他\N{\rEng}we're gonna have to fight him. we can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.64,0:47:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,打他吗？\N{\rEng}Fight him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.18,0:47:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须这么做\N{\rEng}We gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.14,0:47:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们能行的\N{\rEng}It's okay. We can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.44,0:47:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,打架的时候 我们一直是彼此的后盾\N{\rEng}We've always had each other's backs in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.29,0:47:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.57,0:47:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能做到的\N{\rEng}We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.22,0:47:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,声音太大了\N{\rEng}That's gonna make a lot of waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.59,0:47:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没机会了\N{\rEng}We don't have choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.92,0:47:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动\N{\rEng}You hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.92,0:47:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你才别动\N{\rEng}You hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.84,0:48:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们无处可藏了\N{\rEng}You can't hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.61,0:48:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.63,0:48:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 要是换我上 她早就死透了\N{\rEng}Oh my God, if it was me out there, she'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.27,0:48:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 当然是你了\N{\rEng}Yes, of course, it'd be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.91,0:48:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 快点\N{\rEng}Come on, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.87,0:48:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\rEng}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.24,0:48:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住那个婊子\N{\rEng}Get that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.44,0:48:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你\N{\rEng}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要一些酒杯 因为我们要干杯了\N{\rEng}We are gonna need some glasses, cause we're about to have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.99,0:48:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 哈 哈 哈 哈\N{\rEng}Ha ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.95,0:49:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别跑 - 不 不 不 不 不\N{\rEng}- No. - No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.58,0:49:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈是什么？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.93,0:49:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沐浴时间\N{\rEng}Bath time!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.02,0:49:25.20,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}（高温蒸洗）
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.57,0:49:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不 嘿 嘿 嘿\N{\rEng}No, no, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.20,0:49:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\rEng}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.20,0:49:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.08,0:49:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会有手机\N{\rEng}He might have a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.69,0:50:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\rEng}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.69,0:50:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.33,0:50:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}Oh god!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.47,0:50:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.08,0:50:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 天呐\N{\rEng}Okay, Okay, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.60,0:50:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你能帮我吗 求你了\N{\rEng}Can you help me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.63,0:50:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你自己可以的\N{\rEng}No, you got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的很好\N{\rEng}You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.42,0:51:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不行\N{\rEng}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.97,0:51:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会碍事\N{\rEng}I'll just get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.51,0:51:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 看\N{\rEng}Oh, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.23,0:51:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了\N{\rEng}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.74,0:51:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我谢谢你啊\N{\rEng}Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.68,0:51:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\rEng}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.08,0:51:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对你的损失我很抱歉\N{\rEng}I'm so sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.65,0:51:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拉詹先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Rajan?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.13,0:51:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\rEng}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.84,0:51:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拉詹先生 令兄既已仙逝 \N{\rEng}Mr. Rajan, as your brother has left this mortal plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.32,0:51:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,您可以上场了\N{\rEng}you may take the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.31,0:51:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须上场吗？\N{\rEng}Do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.47,0:51:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在所有继承审判中 您的家庭必须由最年长的成员\N{\rEng}Your family must be represented by the eldest member
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.86,0:51:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,或依法指定的家主代表\N{\rEng}or legally appointed head of household in all trials of succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.37,0:51:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,根据第2条第3款C项\N{\rEng}Per Article 2, Section 3, Subsection C.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.96,0:51:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,若不从 则意味着失去勒贝尔先生的庇护\N{\rEng}Failure to do so would mean forfeiture of Mr. LeBail's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.12,0:51:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是说... - 恐怕是的\N{\rEng}- You mean, um... - I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.21,0:52:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老婆怎么样？\N{\rEng}What about my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.64,0:52:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是要放弃拉詹家族族长的身份吗？\N{\rEng}Are you saying you want to abdicate your status as head of the Rajan family?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.39,0:52:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,并且让我老婆狩猎\N{\rEng}And make my wife hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.62,0:52:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.84,0:52:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,（克罗地亚语）操你妈的\N{\rEng}Jebem ti mater da ti jebem.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.67,0:52:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,（克罗地亚语）操你祖宗十八代\N{\rEng}I u pičku maternu i u sto pičke materne.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.27,0:52:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,（克罗地亚语）你个畜生\N{\rEng}Gade jedan gade!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.42,0:52:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,（克罗地亚语）咒你不得好死\N{\rEng}Crko da bog da!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.16,0:52:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\rEng}Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.18,0:52:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请您在上面签个名\N{\rEng}I'll just need you to sign that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.58,0:52:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,马杜 如果你签那个\N{\rEng}Madhu, if you sign that...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.09,0:52:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你死得很惨\N{\rEng}I will make you very dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.35,0:52:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想这样做\N{\rEng}This is hard for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.54,0:52:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不管了\N{\rEng}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.82,0:52:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 没问题\N{\rEng}Okey dokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.68,0:52:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧 女士\N{\rEng}Ma'am, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.15,0:52:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 没问题\N{\rEng}Okey dokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.17,0:52:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,911 你有什么紧急情况\N{\rEng}911, what's your emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.94,0:53:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要帮助 我和我姐姐正在被...\N{\rEng}I need help, my sister and I are being...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.66,0:53:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在在丹福斯赌场\N{\rEng}We're at the Danforth Casino,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.18,0:53:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,高尔夫球场 或者说那个综合设施里\N{\rEng}golf course, whatever, compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.68,0:53:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有人要杀我们\N{\rEng}People are trying to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.15,0:53:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉女士 您能说慢点 并重复一下吗？\N{\rEng}I'm sorry ma'am, could you slow down and repeat yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.43,0:53:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定监控大院内所有外拨电话\N{\rEng}I decided to capture all the outgoing calls on the compound
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.96,0:53:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,以防他们设法弄到电话\N{\rEng}just in case they managed to get their hands on a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.19,0:53:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做的？\N{\rEng}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拥有这家电话公司\N{\rEng}We own the phone company.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.46,0:53:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们全都是崇拜魔鬼的人\N{\rEng}And they're all devil worshippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.81,0:53:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道听起来很荒唐 但我们真的需要帮助\N{\rEng}I know it sounds insane, but we need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.28,0:53:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在在丹福斯度假村 请派人过来\N{\rEng}We're at the Danforth Resort, please send someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.22,0:53:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我知道了\N{\rEng}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.66,0:53:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会立即派人过去帮忙\N{\rEng}We will send help right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.24,0:53:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你能赶到正门吗？\N{\rEng}Can you make it to the main gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.39,0:53:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我们会过去的\N{\rEng}Yeah, we'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.76,0:53:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.63,0:53:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.08,0:53:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.23,0:53:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信吗？\N{\rEng}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.58,0:53:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我确信\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.73,0:53:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会伤害你的\N{\rEng}I'm not here to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.34,0:54:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗 费丝\N{\rEng}Do you hear that Faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.36,0:54:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那个拿剑的女人不是来伤害我们的\N{\rEng}The lady with the sword isn't here to hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.17,0:54:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对的\N{\rEng}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.72,0:54:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想跟你打打杀杀\N{\rEng}I have no desire to get into some punchy, kicky situation with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.62,0:54:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有办法解决这个问题\N{\rEng}There's a way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.59,0:54:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来杀你的\N{\rEng}I'm not here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.93,0:54:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我来这\N{\rEng}I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.03,0:54:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,提出个交易\N{\rEng}to offer you a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.13,0:54:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 怎么说\N{\rEng}Alright, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.98,0:54:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我让我的律师仔细查阅了章程\N{\rEng}I had my lawyers scour the bylaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.81,0:54:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为其他成员不知道这个\N{\rEng}I don't think the other council members know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.73,0:54:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你嫁给一个议会成员\N{\rEng}but if you marry into a high council family,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.30,0:54:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你嫁给我儿子 我们得到席位 而你也能活下去\N{\rEng} if you marry my son, we get the seat and you get to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.13,0:54:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说\N{\rEng}Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.85,0:54:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我向拉贝尔先生发誓\N{\rEng}I swear to Mr. LaBelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.24,0:54:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她同意\N{\rEng}She says yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.31,0:54:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再狩猎了\N{\rEng}No more Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.13,0:54:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再狩猎了\N{\rEng}No more Hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.20,0:54:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道你第一段婚姻结局不太好\N{\rEng}And look, I know your first marriage didn't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.92,0:54:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但我儿子承福不像亚历克斯\N{\rEng}But my Cheng-Fu isn't like Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.80,0:54:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然他是个傻子 但是他很善良\N{\rEng}He's an idiot, but he's kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.89,0:54:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果丹福斯家族不再在幕后操控 世界会好得多\N{\rEng}And the world will be far better off without the Danforths pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.17,0:54:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.70,0:54:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯是个变态疯子\N{\rEng}Titus is a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.57,0:55:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他姐姐控制不了他\N{\rEng}His sister won't be able to control him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.27,0:55:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,世界会比现在更快走向末日\N{\rEng}And the world will go to hell faster than it already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.12,0:55:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是个好人\N{\rEng}But you're a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.83,0:55:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是\N{\rEng}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.84,0:55:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但这只是程度上的差别罢了\N{\rEng}But it's a matter of degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.19,0:55:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那我就这么嫁给了一个陌生人\N{\rEng}Right, okay, so I'm just married to some stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.69,0:55:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 但是 - 太好了\N{\rEng}- Yes, but... - Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.21,0:55:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不必像夫妻一样生活\N{\rEng}You don't have to live as a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.38,0:55:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以做任何你想做的事\N{\rEng}You can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.94,0:55:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对 她会做的\N{\rEng}Yeah, she'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.57,0:55:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.92,0:55:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.34,0:55:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.78,0:55:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不...这也太容易了吧\N{\rEng}No, this seems too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.28,0:55:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不用做吗？\N{\rEng}What, I wouldn't have to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.16,0:55:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.25,0:55:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 她必须做什么\N{\rEng}Okay, well, what would she have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.78,0:55:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,严格来说 她算是组织的一员\N{\rEng}Technically, she'd be part of the organization, but
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.09,0:55:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但她只需要做我们大家都要做的那些常规工作\N{\rEng}she'd just have to do the usual stuff we all have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.92,0:55:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不算太糟 - 那是什么？\N{\rEng}- It's not so bad. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.36,0:55:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那些常规工作？\N{\rEng}What's the usual stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.71,0:55:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是说... - 你是说要献祭山羊 猪之类的？\N{\rEng}- I mean... - You mean sacrificing goats and shit and pigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.99,0:55:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的杀害无辜的人？\N{\rEng}Fucking killing innocent people?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.78,0:55:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,出卖他妈的我的灵魂？\N{\rEng}Selling my fucking soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.23,0:55:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那还是算了\N{\rEng}Yeah, that's gonna be a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.07,0:55:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,（西班牙语）他妈的\N{\rEng}Puta madre.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.09,0:55:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开 伊格纳西奥\N{\rEng}Fuck off, Ignacio!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.23,0:55:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个该死的怪胎\N{\rEng}You fucking weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.53,0:55:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你不能杀我\N{\rEng}You know you can't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.91,0:56:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说同意\N{\rEng}Say yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.71,0:56:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\rEng}Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.17,0:56:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\rEng}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.71,0:56:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不说 我会在他动手之前杀了你\N{\rEng}If you don't, I have to kill you before he does!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.43,0:56:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.21,0:56:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意了\N{\rEng}I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.93,0:56:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会嫁给你那该死的儿子\N{\rEng}I'll marry your fucking son!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.38,0:56:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,晨 快点 让开\N{\rEng}Chen! Hurry up! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.89,0:56:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,说 同意 天呐\N{\rEng}Say yes, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.30,0:56:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就说 同意\N{\rEng}Just say yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.49,0:56:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快说\N{\rEng}Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.84,0:56:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.21,0:56:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.89,0:56:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,晨\N{\rEng}Chen!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.33,0:56:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她会同意的\N{\rEng}She'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.09,0:56:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她会嫁给你那该死的儿子\N{\rEng}She'll marry your fucking son!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.89,0:56:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她必须说\N{\rEng}She has to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.20,0:56:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须说\N{\rEng}You have to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.33,0:56:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\rEng}God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.25,0:57:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么大家都看着我\N{\rEng}Why is everyone looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.94,0:57:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧...\N{\rEng}Okay, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.40,0:57:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我得赶紧弄个新的来\N{\rEng}I'll need a fresh one of these, stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.73,0:57:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 呃 给我件雨披之类的\N{\rEng}And, uh, give me a poncho or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.25,0:57:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 珍\N{\rEng}Thanks, Jen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.49,0:57:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.44,0:57:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.17,0:57:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不习惯有人在我面前自爆\N{\rEng}I'm really not used to people combusting all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.41,0:57:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.57,0:57:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.37,0:57:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,确实总是让人猝不及防\N{\rEng}It's always surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.88,0:58:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么拒绝了\N{\rEng}Why did you say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.82,0:58:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以救我们\N{\rEng}You could have saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.76,0:58:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想后半辈子都他妈地去杀人\N{\rEng}Uh, because I don't want to spend the rest of my life fucking killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.89,0:58:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.31,0:58:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女人出卖了自己的灵魂\N{\rEng}That lady sold her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.37,0:58:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会做同样的事\N{\rEng}I'm not gonna sell mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.35,0:58:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁可去死 也不要那样活着\N{\rEng}I'd rather be dead than live like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.84,0:58:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道为什么我不想冒险吗\N{\rEng}You wanna know why I don't take risks?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.80,0:58:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我冒了一次险\N{\rEng}It's because the one time... I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.47,0:58:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了纽约 结果被耍了 然后\N{\rEng}I got fucked and moved to New York and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.82,0:58:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了你\N{\rEng}and I lost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.77,0:58:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有搬去纽约\N{\rEng}You didn't move to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.01,0:58:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你抛弃了我\N{\rEng}You left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.02,0:59:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝 现在不是提这事的时候\N{\rEng}Faith, we can't do this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.87,0:59:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你本应该可以带我一起走的\N{\rEng}You could have taken me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.07,0:59:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时18岁\N{\rEng}I was 18!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.24,0:59:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一次千载难逢的奖学金机会\N{\rEng}It was a once-iN - a-lifetime scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.58,0:59:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么会... - 我们是一个团队\N{\rEng}- How do you not... - We were a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.69,0:59:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以成为我的法定监护人\N{\rEng}You could have become my legal guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.47,0:59:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时15岁？\N{\rEng}You were 15?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.98,0:59:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么照顾你？\N{\rEng}I couldn't take care of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.91,0:59:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮助付房租\N{\rEng}I could have helped with rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.00,0:59:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么帮\N{\rEng}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.86,0:59:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那里是纽约\N{\rEng}It was New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.05,0:59:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一个孩子\N{\rEng}You were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.09,0:59:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对 你的孩子妹妹\N{\rEng}Yeah, your kid sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.81,0:59:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你\N{\rEng}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.55,0:59:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾有个计划\N{\rEng}I had a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.76,0:59:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我会为我们两个打拼出更好的生活\N{\rEng}I was gonna make a better life for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.96,0:59:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等我毕业了就把你接过来\N{\rEng}I was gonna bring you out once I graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.48,0:59:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那个年纪 三年有多漫长吗？\N{\rEng}Do you know how long three years is at that age?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.66,0:59:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝 你当时还好\N{\rEng}Faith, you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.83,0:59:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你很安全\N{\rEng}You were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.29,0:59:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝...我们的养父母人不坏\N{\rEng}Grace... We had decent foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.30,0:59:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你有个栖身之所\N{\rEng}You had a roof over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.72,0:59:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.72,0:59:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你抛弃了我\N{\rEng}You left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.26,0:59:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你打了好几年电话\N{\rEng}I called you for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.59,0:59:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不接\N{\rEng}You didn't wanna talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.10,0:59:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我那时很生气\N{\rEng}I was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.11,0:59:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤透了我的心\N{\rEng}It broke my fucking heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.33,0:59:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在你伤透我的心之后\N{\rEng}After you broke mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.31,0:59:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得你对我说的最后一句话吗\N{\rEng}You remember the last thing you said to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.53,1:00:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 求你了 不要走 你说...\N{\rEng}I said, please don't go, and you said...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.85,1:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“我必须走”\N{\rEng}"I have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.70,1:00:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,“没有其他选择”\N{\rEng}"There's no other way."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.21,1:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈真的很抱歉\N{\rEng}I'm fucking sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.51,1:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你感到开心\N{\rEng}I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.93,1:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你和你完美的生活感到开心\N{\rEng}I'm very happy for you and your perfect life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.63,1:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,德里克这个人是我编的\N{\rEng}I made up Derek.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.26,1:00:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我住在布什维克\N{\rEng}I live in Bushwick,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.71,1:00:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是什么自媒体人\N{\rEng}and I'm not a social media manager.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.15,1:00:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么的\N{\rEng}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.75,1:00:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个迎宾员\N{\rEng}I'm a hostess.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.35,1:00:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,严格来说 我是服务员 职级比你高\N{\rEng}Technically, as a waitress, I outrank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.75,1:00:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我太好看了 所以让我当迎宾\N{\rEng}They made me a hostess because they said I'm so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.56,1:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 但你拿不到小费\N{\rEng}Yeah, but you don't get any tips.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.41,1:00:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到很多小费 因为我真的很漂亮\N{\rEng}I get a lot of tips because I'm really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.24,1:01:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 我不需要小费 因为我那个假男朋友德里克赚大钱\N{\rEng}Well, I don't need tips because my fake boyfriend Derek makes bank, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.93,1:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对 对 对\N{\rEng}Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.86,1:01:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑德里克\N{\rEng}God bless Derek.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.61,1:01:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.80,1:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.28,1:01:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 你能接那个电话吗\N{\rEng}Shit, can you get that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.99,1:01:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是她们\N{\rEng}It could be them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.03,1:01:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 接 - 我不想接\N{\rEng}- Answer it. - I don't want to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.50,1:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她们不能两次找到同一个911接线员\N{\rEng}They can't get the same 911 operator twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.83,1:01:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈说什么\N{\rEng}The fuck do I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.06,1:01:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧他妈的接就是了\N{\rEng}Just fucking answer it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.90,1:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,911\N{\rEng}911.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.95,1:01:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么紧急情况\N{\rEng}What's your emergency?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.48,1:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到了\N{\rEng}We're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.20,1:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,警察在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where are the cops?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.92,1:01:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪儿？\N{\rEng}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.11,1:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们沿着墙走向正门\N{\rEng}We're following a wall to the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.76,1:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到警车\N{\rEng}I don't see a cop car.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.62,1:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,警察在附近\N{\rEng}The unit is close.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.33,1:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,待在大门附近 他们会看见你的\N{\rEng}Just wait there at the gate, and they will see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.96,1:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你个婊子\N{\rEng}You bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.53,1:02:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,料到了吗？\N{\rEng}Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.60,1:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮\N{\rEng}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.72,1:02:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我们一听就知道是你的声音 他妈的蠢货\N{\rEng}So, we knew it was your voice on the phone, fucking dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.34,1:02:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对 白痴\N{\rEng}Yeah, idiots.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.64,1:02:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在监视你\N{\rEng}We've been watching you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.92,1:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行\N{\rEng}Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.94,1:02:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 嗯 告诉我们怎么开门\N{\rEng}All right, well, tell us how to open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.62,1:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能在控制室操作\N{\rEng}Well, you can only do that from the control room.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.31,1:02:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们如何到那\N{\rEng}How do we get there?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.52,1:02:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.07,1:02:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你回去 左转\N{\rEng}Well, you go back inside, you make a left.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.75,1:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,最右侧的那部电梯是唯一一部\N{\rEng}The elevator on the far right is the only one
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.98,1:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,通往地下二层的电梯\N{\rEng}that descends to the sub-basement.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.33,1:02:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,右转 进入控制室\N{\rEng}You make a right, you go into the control room.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.15,1:02:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,当你进去后\N{\rEng}When you're inside...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.06,1:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己想办法吧\N{\rEng}you fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.01,1:02:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我们如何打开它\N{\rEng}Tell us how to open it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.20,1:02:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不告诉你\N{\rEng}I don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.04,1:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我们怎么开门 否则我们杀了你哥哥\N{\rEng}Tell us how to open the gate, or we're gonna kill your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.10,1:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,随便\N{\rEng}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.14,1:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他\N{\rEng}Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.50,1:02:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我没在开玩笑\N{\rEng}I'm not fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.77,1:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rEng}Yeah, me neither.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.79,1:02:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了 至高位就是我的了\N{\rEng}Him out of the way, the seat's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.11,1:02:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真是冷血\N{\rEng}Well, that's some cold blooded shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.12,1:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 谁抛弃了谁？\N{\rEng}So, who abandoned who?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.80,1:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？\N{\rEng}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.31,1:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当年\N{\rEng}Back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.37,1:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\rEng}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.61,1:03:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你 对吗？\N{\rEng}You, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.47,1:03:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是姐姐\N{\rEng}You're older.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.33,1:03:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她今天一整天都在拖你后腿\N{\rEng}She's just been holding you back all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.51,1:03:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她还会再次抛弃你的 对吧？\N{\rEng}You know she's gonna leave you again, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.31,1:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上你的狗嘴\N{\rEng}Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.19,1:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,敢打我\N{\rEng}Fucking hit me!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.18,1:03:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.05,1:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊\N{\rEng}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.55,1:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对 对 撞死她\N{\rEng}Yes, yes, run her down!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.07,1:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的婊子\N{\rEng}That's my bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.37,1:03:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别被撞死了\N{\rEng}Get out of the road!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.60,1:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\rEng}What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.70,1:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她已经走了 老兄\N{\rEng}I think she's leaving, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.77,1:03:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\rEng}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.60,1:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.73,1:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝 快跑\N{\rEng}Faith, Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.57,1:03:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.35,1:04:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rEng}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.81,1:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,跑\N{\rEng}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.71,1:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃吧 格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Give it up, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.06,1:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最好的结局\N{\rEng}This is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,滚吧你\N{\rEng}Get the fuck off her!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.15,1:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.07,1:04:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 起来\N{\rEng}One, two, three, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.27,1:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧\N{\rEng}Okay, alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.10,1:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦天呐\N{\rEng}Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.32,1:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要上高尔夫球车\N{\rEng}We're gonna get into a golf cart!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.46,1:04:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.56,1:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走 走\N{\rEng}Let's go. let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.80,1:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,“杀了他”\N{\rEng}"Kill him."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.26,1:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“我不在意”\N{\rEng}"I don't care."
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.01,1:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在拖延时间 白痴\N{\rEng}I was stalling, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.38,1:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定对你做了不少事\N{\rEng}I surely did a number on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.90,1:05:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看...\N{\rEng}You look at the...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.90,1:05:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别他妈把我当小孩子\N{\rEng}Stop treating me like I'm a fucking child.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.46,1:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.37,1:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好上场了\N{\rEng}I am ready to take the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.35,1:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上你不被允许上场\N{\rEng}You're not allowed to, actually.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.84,1:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你放弃了\N{\rEng}You abdicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.61,1:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不再是家族的族长了\N{\rEng}You're no longer the head of your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.85,1:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你的妻子控制着你所有的资产\N{\rEng}And your wife controls all of your assets.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.31,1:05:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,即使她选择不参与狩猎 她仍然代表你的家族\N{\rEng}Even though she's chosen not to hunt, she still represents your family.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.78,1:05:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.36,1:05:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你一无所有\N{\rEng}You own nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.58,1:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 呃\N{\rEng}I think, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.80,1:06:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我需要躺下\N{\rEng}I think I need to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.66,1:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你兄弟的遗骸该送到哪里？\N{\rEng}Where shall I send your brother's remains?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.36,1:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,送去你妈的屁眼里\N{\rEng}To your mother's asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.50,1:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你这混蛋\N{\rEng}You fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.09,1:06:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,睡个好觉\N{\rEng}Have a nice nap.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.33,1:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,操你\N{\rEng}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.82,1:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你\N{\rEng}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.03,1:06:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你 你这变态小杂种\N{\rEng}And fuck you, you creepy little fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.79,1:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈的恨死你们了\N{\rEng}I fucking hate all of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.19,1:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你也去死吧\N{\rEng}Fuck you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.52,1:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.29,1:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你一点都不难过\N{\rEng}That's not at all sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.75,1:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好了\N{\rEng}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.07,1:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,给我那该死的笔\N{\rEng}Give me the fucking pen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.99,1:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.26,1:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快 跑 跑 跑\N{\rEng}Come on, run, run, run.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.43,1:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说了要跑\N{\rEng}told you to fucking run.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.19,1:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\N{\rEng}Just sit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.29,1:07:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让我帮你拔出来\N{\rEng}Let me...let me help pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.69,1:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,必须拔出来\N{\rEng}It's gotta come out!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.25,1:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我去给你找点止痛的东西\N{\rEng}I'm gonna find you something for the pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.23,1:07:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.24,1:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要辣椒喷雾吗？\N{\rEng}There's pepper spray.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.16,1:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑子蠢吗？\N{\rEng}You don't think?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.58,1:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你听不懂人话吗？\N{\rEng}You don't listen?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.40,1:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所有选项摆在你面前\N{\rEng}Out of all the options in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.44,1:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你偏偏次次都选最蠢的那个\N{\rEng}you always manage to pick the dumbest one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.65,1:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害啊\N{\rEng}It's actually impressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.78,1:08:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么每次都能那么蠢的\N{\rEng}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.86,1:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了你\N{\rEng}I saved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.01,1:08:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来可以自救的\N{\rEng}You could have saved yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.10,1:08:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可以去找救援\N{\rEng}You could have gotten help.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.05,1:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我照顾不了我们俩\N{\rEng}I can't take care of both of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.72,1:08:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的做不到\N{\rEng}I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.76,1:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 都是我的错\N{\rEng}Oh, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.46,1:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我真是个累赘\N{\rEng}And I know. I'm such a burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.33,1:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是个孩子\N{\rEng}You're a fucking child!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.40,1:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈来这里唯一的原因就是你\N{\rEng}The only reason I'm fucking here is because of you,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.14,1:08:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在我他妈要死在这里也是因为你\N{\rEng}and now I'm gonna fucking die here because of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.51,1:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我 你几小时前就死了\N{\rEng}You would have died hours ago if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.86,1:08:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 抱歉我没跑掉把你扔下 但这事儿更像你的作风\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm sorry I didn't run away and abandon you, but that's more your thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.00,1:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我离开是对的\N{\rEng}I was right to fucking leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.31,1:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望你他妈从没找到我\N{\rEng}And I wish you never goddamn found me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.38,1:08:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\rEng}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.27,1:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该跑的\N{\rEng}I should have run.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.62,1:08:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\rEng}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.76,1:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,滚吧\N{\rEng}And fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.23,1:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,费丝 等等\N{\rEng}Faith, wait!
