Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.10,1:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能得到席位...\N{\rEng}you get your seat...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.25,1:20:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而我也能活下去\N{\rEng}and I get to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.22,1:20:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道我们能不能在天亮前把她弄出来\N{\rEng}Don't know if we'll be able to get her out before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.21,1:21:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的\N{\rEng}Fuck it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.88,1:21:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受你的求婚\N{\rEng}I accept your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.21,1:21:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.96,1:21:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.70,1:21:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rEng}Okay, Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.21,1:21:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.46,1:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先得到一些保证 这样我才放心\N{\rEng}I'm going to need some assurances first so I know
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.75,1:21:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我出来的时候 你可别把我们俩都杀了\N{\rEng}you're not just going to kill us both when I come out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.71,1:21:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你发誓...哦 别向我发誓\N{\rEng}I swear to you... Oh, don't swear to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.83,1:21:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的白痴\N{\rEng}Fucking shit for brains!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.07,1:21:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,向勒贝尔先生发誓\N{\rEng}Swear to Mr. LeBail!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.75,1:21:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我向勒贝尔先生发誓 不会伤害你或你妹妹\N{\rEng}I swear to Mr. LeBail that no harm shall come to you or your sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.48,1:21:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能\N{\rEng}You can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.06,1:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\rEng}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.89,1:22:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让人把你需要的一切都拿来\N{\rEng}I'll have everything you need brought in.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.19,1:22:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,做好准备\N{\rEng}Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.17,1:22:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,参加加冕典礼的宾客已经陆续抵达\N{\rEng}The guests are already arriving for coronation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.07,1:23:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们不妨干杯庆祝一下\N{\rEng}I thought maybe we could have a toast.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.52,1:23:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就要成为一家人了\N{\rEng}We're about to become family.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.23,1:24:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我从没想伤害你\N{\rEng}Grace, I never wanted to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.01,1:24:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我必须遵守规则\N{\rEng}But I had to follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.72,1:24:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我们时间不多了\N{\rEng}Listen, we don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.99,1:24:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就直说了\N{\rEng}So I'm just gonna say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.74,1:24:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕\N{\rEng}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.72,1:24:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥\N{\rEng}It's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.02,1:24:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\rEng}I didn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.62,1:24:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底是谁\N{\rEng}who he really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.18,1:24:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了一辈子\N{\rEng}I spent my whole life...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.11,1:24:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找他身上的优点\N{\rEng}searching for the good in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.89,1:24:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我找到了什么\N{\rEng}You know what I found?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.14,1:24:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.74,1:24:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈什么也没有\N{\rEng}Absolutely fucking nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.23,1:24:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我能控制住他\N{\rEng}I thought I could keep him in check.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.44,1:24:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但他已经失控了\N{\rEng}But he's lost it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.86,1:24:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝 我需要你的帮助\N{\rEng}Grace, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.97,1:24:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须一起努力控制他\N{\rEng}We have to try to control him together.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.59,1:24:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有一个席位不见得就是坏事\N{\rEng}Having a seat doesn't have to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.19,1:25:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想想我们能用那种权力做多少好事\N{\rEng}Think about all the good we could do with that power.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.03,1:25:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但我需要你在我身边\N{\rEng}But I need you at my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.69,1:25:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Hey, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.48,1:25:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你不像我们\N{\rEng}You're not like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.74,1:25:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你有希望\N{\rEng}You have hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.58,1:25:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在没有\N{\rEng}I don't now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.16,1:25:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是你夺走了它\N{\rEng}You took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.17,1:25:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很擅长这个\N{\rEng}We are good at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.87,1:25:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来点姐妹时间\N{\rEng}A little girl time.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.45,1:26:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你让我看清了你的真面目\N{\rEng}Thank you for showing me who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.66,1:26:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯 听我解释...\N{\rEng}Titus, it's not a ...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.20,1:26:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯 停下\N{\rEng}Titus, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.59,1:26:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想控制我\N{\rEng}You want to control me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.96,1:26:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.82,1:26:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要所有的权力\N{\rEng}You want all the power for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.10,1:26:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.03,1:26:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你想\N{\rEng}You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.68,1:26:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是这么想的\N{\rEng}You do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.26,1:26:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这样\N{\rEng}You always do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.35,1:26:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是这样\N{\rEng}You always do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.20,1:26:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯 停下 求你了\N{\rEng}Titus stop, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.22,1:26:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我 格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Look at me, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.81,1:26:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我 格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.82,1:26:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让她看着我\N{\rEng}Get her to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.32,1:26:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看到这个 格蕾丝\N{\rEng}I want you to see this, Grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.08,1:26:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看到这个\N{\rEng}I want you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.20,1:26:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,格蕾丝\N{\rEng}Grace!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.06,1:26:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看到我是谁\N{\rEng}I want you to see who I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.45,1:26:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你看清楚 我不是一个可以被人掌控的人\N{\rEng}I want you to see that I am not a man who can be controlled.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.09,1:26:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你提到了规则\N{\rEng}You mentioned the rules.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.71,1:26:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,规则里没有关于杀害家族成员的内容\N{\rEng}There's nothing in the rules about killing a family member.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.22,1:26:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来试试控制我啊\N{\rEng}Try to keep me in check now.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.48,1:27:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看\N{\rEng}Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.48,1:27:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你 会是我抓住你\N{\rEng}I told you it would be me who got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.54,1:27:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们祭坛见\N{\rEng}I'll see you at the altar.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.16,1:29:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能...这么做\N{\rEng}You can't...do this
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.94,1:29:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须这么做\N{\rEng}I have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.05,1:29:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没有别的办法\N{\rEng}There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.11,1:29:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.25,1:30:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢姆·汉普拉\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.78,1:30:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈什么都看不见\N{\rEng}I can't see shit move.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.81,1:30:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,至高无上的撒旦路西法之名\N{\rEng}Nomine satani Lucifer excelsis.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.78,1:30:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奉我们伟大而永恒的恩主之名\N{\rEng}In the name of our great and eternal benefactor,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.37,1:30:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请现身 赐福予众人\N{\rEng}come forth and bestow your blessing upon these.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.39,1:30:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,以撒旦 路西法 巴利尔 利维坦之名\N{\rEng}In the names of Satan, Lucifer, Baliel, Leviathan,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.81,1:30:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现身并作证\N{\rEng}come forth and bear witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.84,1:30:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.06,1:30:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.06,1:30:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎 各位\N{\rEng}Welcome, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.32,1:30:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴有这么多人能来\N{\rEng}I'm pleased so many of you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.27,1:30:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅在这个美好的早晨举行加冕仪式\N{\rEng}Not only do we have our coronation this fine morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.86,1:30:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有一场婚礼\N{\rEng}we also have a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.91,1:30:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的福杯满盈\N{\rEng}Our cup runneth over.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.45,1:31:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯\N{\rEng}Titus.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.27,1:31:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请伸出你的手\N{\rEng}Your hand, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.20,1:32:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你们的誓言是出于本意 且受撒旦之力所驱使\N{\rEng}Your vows being made by intent, by the power of Satan,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.23,1:32:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在宣布你们彼此归属\N{\rEng}I now confer the possession of each other upon you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.87,1:32:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯·切斯特·丹福斯\N{\rEng}Titus Chester Danforth.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.03,1:32:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意娶这位女士 并承诺与她共度今生与来世吗？\N{\rEng}Do you take this woman, in this world and the next?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.82,1:32:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是下地狱的烈火？\N{\rEng}Unto the fires of hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.16,1:32:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\rEng}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.23,1:32:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而你 格蕾丝·伊丽莎白·麦考利·勒多马斯 愿意接受这个男人\N{\rEng}And do you, Grace Elizabeth MacCaullay Le Domas, take this man to be yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.79,1:32:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在肉体和精神上 并承诺与他共度今生与来世吗？\N{\rEng}In flesh and spirit, in this world and the next?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.31,1:32:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是下地狱的烈火？\N{\rEng}Unto the fires of hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.97,1:32:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\rEng}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.09,1:32:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他在地狱中锻造之物 任凭凡人休想拆解\N{\rEng}What he hath forged in hell, let no mortal tear asunder.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.62,1:32:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊 我们奉你的名祈求\N{\rEng}We ask this in thy name, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.53,1:33:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在宣布你们结为夫妻\N{\rEng}I now pronounce you man and wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.15,1:33:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以亲吻新娘了\N{\rEng}You may kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.23,1:33:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,泰特斯·丹福斯 特此授予利贝西亚议会至高席位\N{\rEng}Titus Danforth, is hereby granted the high seat of the council of Libecia.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.14,1:33:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.09,1:33:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.01,1:33:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.02,1:33:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.13,1:33:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 撒旦万岁 - 撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}- Hail Satan! - Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.43,1:33:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 撒旦万岁 - 撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}- Hail Satan! - Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.15,1:34:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 撒旦万岁 - 撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}- Hail Satan! - Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.90,1:34:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 撒旦万岁 - 撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}- Hail Satan! - Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.75,1:34:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.80,1:34:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死自己的家族成员不违反规则\N{\rEng}It's not against the rules to kill a family member.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.56,1:34:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你的提醒\N{\rEng}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.42,1:34:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是我抓住了你\N{\rEng}It's me who got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.48,1:35:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈发生了什么\N{\rEng}the fuck is happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.17,1:35:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下\N{\rEng}Get on your knees!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.43,1:35:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.72,1:35:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.14,1:35:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.97,1:35:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.19,1:35:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.00,1:35:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我可以为所欲为 对吧\N{\rEng}This means I can do whatever I want, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.95,1:36:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对的\N{\rEng}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.78,1:36:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以领导这个组织\N{\rEng}I could lead this organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.05,1:36:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以改变世界\N{\rEng}I could change the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.28,1:36:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 作为我担任最高委员会主席后的第一项举措\N{\rEng}So as my first act as the head of your high council
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.52,1:36:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我特此宣布将我自己\N{\rEng}I hereby remove myself
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.90,1:36:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,从这个委员会 以及这整个他妈的组织中移除\N{\rEng}from the council and this entire fucking organization!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.99,1:36:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟 她可以那样做吗\N{\rEng}Bro, can she even do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.81,1:36:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,出人意料的是 章程对此几乎只字未提\N{\rEng}There's surprisingly little language about this in the bylaws,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.49,1:36:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没有人相信会有人愿意主动放弃如此大的权力\N{\rEng}since no one believed anyone would ever willingly give away so much power.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.62,1:36:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但然后谁得到那个该死的席位\N{\rEng}Okay, but then who gets the fucking seat?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.32,1:36:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明前谁戴着戒指就是谁\N{\rEng}Whoever's wearing the ring by dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.23,1:36:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明什么时候\N{\rEng}When's dawn?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.24,1:37:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大约三分钟后\N{\rEng}In three minutes, give or take.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.14,1:37:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有议会家族还是\N{\rEng}But it's just the council families or...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.82,1:37:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,严格来说任何人\N{\rEng}Literally anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.57,1:37:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而你说如果黎明前没人戴戒指 勒贝尔先生会\N{\rEng}And you said if no one's wearing the ring by dawn, Mr. LeBail would be...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.00,1:37:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不高兴\N{\rEng}Very upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.40,1:37:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不高兴\N{\rEng}Very upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.94,1:37:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去吃屎吧 你们这些近亲繁殖的混蛋\N{\rEng}Choke on it, you inbred fucks!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.78,1:37:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 我的真神\N{\rEng}I'm coming, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.54,1:37:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舍姆·哈姆·法拉什\N{\rEng}Shem HaMephorash!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.19,1:37:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,撒旦万岁\N{\rEng}Hail Satan!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.32,1:37:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,操 操 操 操\N{\rEng}Fuck, fuck, fuck, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.63,1:38:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哇\N{\rEng}Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.99,1:38:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会杀了你的\N{\rEng}I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.86,1:38:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,操...\N{\rEng}Fucking...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.34,1:38:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总得有人把这一切付之一炬\N{\rEng}Someone had to burn it all down.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.10,1:38:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你很擅长毁掉一切\N{\rEng}You are good at destroying things.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.49,1:38:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你自由了\N{\rEng}You're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.28,1:38:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rEng}See ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.54,1:38:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\rEng}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.77,1:38:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你好呀\N{\rEng}Hi, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.70,1:38:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 对 别看那里\N{\rEng}Hey, yeah, don't look there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.03,1:38:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟\N{\rEng}Oops
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.08,1:40:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,操 太爽了\N{\rEng}Fuck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.94,1:40:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着 婊子们\N{\rEng}I'm alive, bitches!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.75,1:40:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还活着\N{\rEng}We made it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.90,1:40:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还活着\N{\rEng}We made it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.55,1:40:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我了个大草\N{\rEng}Holy fucking shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.86,1:40:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经脱离了组织 所以才幸免于难\N{\rEng}I've renounced my pack, so I've been spared too!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.86,1:40:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们他妈的开派对\N{\rEng}Let's fucking party!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.35,1:40:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\rEng}Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.28,1:41:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁？\N{\rEng}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.72,1:41:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咩\N{\rEng}Meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.46,1:41:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能走了吗\N{\rEng}Can we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.52,1:41:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,咩\N{\rEng}Meow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.34,1:41:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.44,1:41:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你玩火箭筒\N{\rEng}Rocket launcher.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.14,1:42:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来 我们走\N{\rEng}Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.25,1:42:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.57,1:42:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\rEng}I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.39,1:42:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你了\N{\rEng}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.37,1:42:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 不过你知道 以后我不必再这么想了\N{\rEng}Yeah, well, you know, I'm not gonna have to anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.20,1:42:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你会他妈烦死我的\N{\rEng}You're gonna get really fucking sick of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.26,1:42:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,保证？\N{\rEng}Promise?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.10,1:43:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\rEng}I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.19,1:43:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么处理那只山羊？\N{\rEng}What are you gonna do with the goat?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.34,1:43:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.38,1:43:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你这周打算结几次婚？\N{\rEng}How many times are you gonna get married this week?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.08,1:43:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太快了\N{\rEng}It's too soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.52,1:43:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定破纪录了\N{\rEng}It's gotta be a record.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.41,1:43:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.42,1:43:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去医院\N{\rEng}We're gonna go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.70,1:43:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去洗个澡\N{\rEng}I need a bath.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.82,1:43:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也感觉快臭了\N{\rEng}I stink too.
